          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A high-purity germanium(HPGe) gamma-ray",
                "detector associated  with a digital gamma",
                "spectrometry system (ORTECDSPEC TM)  and Maestro data",
                "acquisition software was used to measure radioactivity.",
                "Radioactivity of the  115mIn and 198Au were measured",
                "nondestructively at the Institute of Nuclear  Science",
                "and Technology(INST), Savar, Dhaka, Bangladesh.",
                " The radioactivities of the relatively long-lived",
                "radionuclides  54Mn, 59Fe, 58Co, 92mNb and 114mIn were",
                "measured using a low  level HPGe  gamma-ray detector",
                "at the Institute fur Nuklearchemie, Forschungszentrum",
                "Julich, Germany.",
                "The efficiency versus  energy curve of the HPGe",
                "gamma-ray detector was determined  using the standard",
                "point sources 22Na, 57Co, 60Co, 133Ba, 137Cs,  152Eu",
                "and 226Ra."
              ]
            }
